<h2 class="zm-item-title zm-editable-content">

<a href="/question/19697709">面对强奸，女性如何保护自己？</a>

</h2>
</div>
<div id="zh-question-detail" class="zm-item-rich-text" data-resourceid="59074" data-action="/question/detail">

<div class="zm-editable-content"><p>刚看到一条新闻，<a href="http://news.sina.com.cn/s/2014-06-26/182830428099.shtml" class=" wrap external" target="_blank" rel="nofollow noreferrer">女汉子揪住命根制服强奸歹徒 民警称赞有勇有谋<i class="icon-external"></i></a></p></div>


